race.comment: MARSHALL BEAR (4) drew the inside and won last time at Geelong over 460m (25.83) after forging to the front and leading throughout, scoring by 2 lengths. The one to beat again. PAW DROGO (1) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when third (24.23) in a Grade 5 at Bendigo. Can improve sharply here. BABY GIRL PEARL (7) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (25.71) last time in a Grade 4/5 at Warrnambool. Solid record at the distance winning three races. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Can do much better this time. PAPA EASY (2) placed last time and cannot be ignored.
